snippet.title: Company of Heroes 3 - Console Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Company of Heroes 3 is coming to console! Full controller support, custom console UI, and features that allow you to play at your own pace, will make for an incredible strategy experience on PS5 and Xbox Series S and X.

Find out more on our website: https://www.companyofheroes.com/en/company-of-heroes-3-console-edition

You have questions about the announcement? Check out our F.A.Q. ► https://bit.ly/3W57jH2
